{"tid":2059020,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［真相大白］肥佬黎口中嘅鬼係李柱銘？","createTime":"2020-06-10T14:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T04:10:54.000Z","uid":69221,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fd1eacf6331a3ee730a913d4407ad025796edabb","tid":2059020,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"李柱銘: 年輕時支持「港獨」, 後來轉而支持「民主回歸」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058702\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058702</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLRDmR0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLRDmR0.jpg&h=e6e10710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎智英：港獨當年係有鬼背後推動， 當時我已經叫唔好中計！(2020-4-27)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004351\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004351</a><br />\n<br />\n黎智英:<br />\n<br />\n港獨當年係有鬼背後推動， 當時我已經叫唔好中計！<br />\n聽說一些鼓吹港獨的知名人士，都是習帝權鬥對手促使，想在香港製造大災難，逼中共派解放軍入城鎮壓，掀起自由世界對中國經濟和政治制裁，給今日面對四面楚歌危機四伏之際的習帝添麻煩，我們必須小心。位於中共極權危牆之下，港獨不但無可能，<span style=\"color: red;\">我們更會失去了國際和市民的支持，是死路一條！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7090d550f59e171c11431e206e04f827a27e1ec6","tid":2059020,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:49:37.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"a9df1981b89c88bdfa6d25741e1ccd12f1363dfd","tid":2059020,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd7c0e214517cc91f0cc562e5cfb981bc6780b0","tid":2059020,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274efd16e2de7be2158f452f9daf90951c182358","tid":2059020,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac