:2059020,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90758ff31c0e6a3a31f8c3b7923fb7a67840a1f6","tid":2059020,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"李柱銘係灰線既共諜來, 中共點會肯俾d真正反對派坐係基本法草案委員會入面呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"或者係立場唔會威脅到政權 先會比佢入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"永遠既投降派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢起個黨就咁寫既:<br />\n<br />\n民主黨的基本信念<br />\n1. 香港是中國不可分割的一部分，我們支持香港回歸中國。<br />\n<br />\n中共國既憲法第一條:<br />\n中華人民共和國是工人階級領導的、以工農聯盟為基礎的人民民主專政的社會主義國家。<br />\n<br />\n社會主義制度是中華人民共和國的根本制度。中國共產黨領導是中國特色社會主義最本質的特征。禁止任何組織或者個人破壞社會主義制度。<br />\n<br />\n係咪即係呢條友支持一黨專政既香港, or else佢就係想顛覆國家?佢承認得基本法第一條就必須要accept中共係佢既領導<br />\n<br />\n定係李柱銘既中國唔係中共國係中華民國定係想另立新中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d62ea371d487cbce68a0f4cd8927d1b5285ed7e","tid":2059020,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5f11b13f6a1839734155409c7e6cb689993a357","tid":2059020,"uid":108359,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"已經垂死 仲要內鬥 拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"係囉，中國已經垂死，香港人仲要搞分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梗係民主回歸獻中華啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93dbbd6bd8af82711f4cee68da17fcd3f9bc06c","tid":2059020,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f3da51993726dfb787c0d51cb00a9cc568bdb7","tid":2059020,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s